title: CD19+/CD20+ B cells 1, scRNA-seq
extract_protocol_ch1: Chromium Single Cell 5’ Library & Gel Bead Kit, Chromium Next GEM Single Cell 5’ Library & Gel Bead Kit v1.1, following manufacturer’s protocol
description: Sample was prepared using the Next GEM Single Cell 5’ kit v1.1, sequenced using NovaSeq, and aligned using Cell Ranger v5.0
data_processing: The resulting scRNA-seq data were processed with CellRanger (version 2.1, 3.0, and 5.0, 10x Genomics) and mapped to the hg38 reference genome.
